org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.utilities

Class VirtualTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.utilities.VirtualTime

  • public class VirtualTime
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows to simulate a clock. This class belongs to the utilities package because it's meant to be usable on its own if needed (as a library).
